products.name: Basohli Pashmina (shaul)
products.description: Udhampur: Basohli Pashmina:While pashmina shawls are renowned across India, Udhampur takes pride in its Basohli Pashmina.  Made from the incredibly soft and fine underfurs of Changthangi goats, these shawls are known for their exceptional quality, warmth, and delicate feel.  The weaving techniques employed in Basohli create beautiful and intricate designs, making these shawls a luxurious and treasured possession.  Basohli Pashmina has also been awarded a GI tag, signifying its unique characteristics and origin.
